An awesome way to end an awesome year, I say. This Christmas is clearly to the awesome things...\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/lokisky_walker/4196132583/"><img class="aligncenter" alt="An awesome shot don''t you think?" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2644/4196132583_76914df496_b.jpg" width="614" height="461" /></a></p>\nAwesome. Awesome. Awesome. It''s my mantra for the day. Have an awesome merry Christmas!', 'Awesome Things', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '43-revision-2', '', '', '2012-12-22 19:45:35', '2012-12-22 19:45:35', '', 43, 'http://localhost/skytreader.net/43-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
